            "value" : "Purpose: configures Capabilities To Add. Upstream default: see the embedded Apple contract. Accepted values or format: Linux capability name, ALL; validation grammar: ^(ALL|CAP_[A-Z0-9_]+|[A-Z0-9_]+)$. Repeat and order behavior: follows the embedded cardinality and preserves user order. Dependencies and conflicts: enforced from the reviewed contract before dispatch. OS, hardware, and runtime limits: macOS 26, Apple silicon, Apple container 1.1.0. Security or data impact: mutating; required: false. Example: choose a reviewed value in this field. Recovery: correct the highlighted value and retry; MacContainer never applies an invalid value."
