            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Purpose: configures Debug. Upstream default: see the embedded Apple contract. Accepted values or format: ; validation grammar: the reviewed value type. Repeat and order behavior: follows the embedded cardinality and preserves user order. Dependencies and conflicts: enforced from the reviewed contract before dispatch. OS, hardware, and runtime limits: macOS 26, Apple silicon, Apple container 1.1.0. Security or data impact: readOnly; required: false. Example: choose a reviewed value in this field. Recovery: correct the highlighted value and retry; MacContainer never applies an invalid value."
